Class ExportLocations

java.lang.Object
codeContext.processors.export.ExportLocation
codeContext.processors.export.ExportLocations
public class ExportLocations extends ExportLocation
The collection of exported objects from one particular file location (name) -more export locations can be stored inside under one file location (name)
